('Yet what of the lesser golems, those baked from mud and clay and the detritus of the streets. The silent servants that perform the tasks that no one else wants to. Who knows what faces adorn these pitiless creatures? Ask all you want. For all the words written in the heads, none will ever emerge from their lips.', 'LOC_PEDIA_BUILDINGS_PAGE_SLTH_BUILDING_SCULPTORS_STUDIO_CHAPTER_HISTORY_PARA_3', 'en_US'),
('He didn''t speak, but his eyes stared into my face, trying to find some compassion. It was a rare commodity in this world.', 'LOC_PEDIA_LEADERS_PAGE_SLTH_LEADER_TEBRYN_CHAPTER_HISTORY_PARA_11', 'en_US'),
('"Of course, I am always amazed at the beauty of the Unseelie court, and the courtesy of its residents." ', 'LOC_PEDIA_LEADERS_PAGE_SLTH_LEADER_ARENDEL_CHAPTER_HISTORY_PARA_4', 'en_US'),
('"The daft creature is attempting to summon more of its kin." Bradeline looked almost disappointed. "Most would attempt to flee, but both attempts will be blocked by the summoning circle you constructed. Its call can not penetrate the shell of sorcery, symbols and the enchanted powder."', 'LOC_PEDIA_UNITS_PAGE_SLTH_UNIT_MESHABBER_CHAPTER_HISTORY_PARA_9', 'en_US'),
('[H1]Alignment[\H1]', 'LOC_PEDIA_CONCEPTS_PAGE_ALIGNMENT_CHAPTER_CONTENT_PARA_1', 'en_US'),
('Great Engineers can be used to hurry a Wonder''s production, or added to a city for GPP points and Production.', 'LOC_SLTH_UNIT_GREAT_ENGINEER_DESCRIPTION', 'en_US'),
('The farmer only replied, ''Who is to say what is good and what is evil?''', 'LOC_PEDIA_LEADERS_PAGE_SLTH_LEADER_ETHNE_CHAPTER_HISTORY_PARA_17', 'en_US'),
('Soul Forge', 'LOC_SLTH_BUILDING_SOUL_FORGE_NAME', 'en_US'),
('"Well, what gifts have been given to us by dear ol'' Bhall tonight?" The deep voice came from an orc man who pushed past the crowd of orc children eating and playing by the flames near the humans. Unlike the smooth skinned younger orcs, long bone spikes protruded from his back, shoulders, and arms. "Metal blades on young girls? Take your spears, my clan." The burly orc hefted a massive axe and grinned at Capria. Others came forth, wielding long wooden spears.', 'LOC_PEDIA_LEADERS_PAGE_SLTH_LEADER_CAPRIA_CHAPTER_HISTORY_PARA_12', 'en_US'),
('Parih was unable to answer. The demon smirked.', 'LOC_PEDIA_UNITS_PAGE_SLTH_UNIT_ARS_CHAPTER_HISTORY_PARA_8', 'en_US'),
('[H1]Undercouncil[\H1]', 'LOC_PEDIA_CONCEPTS_PAGE_UNDERCOUNCIL_CHAPTER_CONTENT_PARA_1', 'en_US'),
