('+10[ICON_Strength] Combat Strength while on Snow and Tundra.', 'LOC_WINTERBORN_ABILITY_TUNDRA_SNOW_STRENGTH_DESCRIPTION', 'en_US'),
('Guerilla II', 'LOC_PROMOTION_GUERILLA2_NAME', 'en_US'),
('The Demagog is designed for fast mobilization, costing half as much as a champion. But they will abandon you when the crusade is over.', 'LOC_SLTH_UNIT_DEMAGOG_DESCRIPTION', 'en_US'),
('Unit Stoneskin Ogre', 'LOC_SLTH_TRAIT_CIVILIZATION_UNIT_STONESKIN_OGRE_NAME', 'en_US'),
('He didn''t try to include Thessa in the spell. She was looking through piles of ancient tomes when he entered the room. She still had the golden feather in her hair.', 'LOC_PEDIA_BUILDINGS_PAGE_BUILDING_MADRASA_CHAPTER_HISTORY_PARA_78', 'en_US'),
('Don''t let the name fool you, Dragon Slayers are proficient fighters against human opponents as well, and their courage promotion takes some burden off of your spell casters.', 'LOC_SLTH_UNIT_DRAGON_SLAYER_DESCRIPTION', 'en_US'),
('The elven children gathered closer to the storyteller. They could still feel the stirring of their bonds with the forest, but the forests they knew were tombs compared to the forest in the Age of Dragons. The elves still felt deep reverence for them, but the soul of the forest was gone.', 'LOC_PEDIA_UNITS_PAGE_SLTH_UNIT_FAWN_CHAPTER_HISTORY_PARA_3', 'en_US'),
('Gilden had trained most of his life for this. An elf who enjoyed warfare was now witness to his people''s attack, but he was already too late. Maybe if he had arrived an hour before there would have been a chance to kill them before so many new werewolves were born. Maybe if the man wasn''t here. Gilden would fight them, but not here; he had a lot more training to do. So he turned his back on the fighting, left the village and his people''s screams behind him. They would be avenged, but not today.', 'LOC_PEDIA_UNITS_PAGE_SLTH_UNIT_GILDEN_CHAPTER_HISTORY_PARA_5', 'en_US'),
('Jewels', 'LOC_RESOURCE_JEWELS', 'en_US'),
('Unit Goblin', 'LOC_SLTH_TRAIT_CIVILIZATION_UNIT_GOBLIN_NAME', 'en_US'),
('+10% Bonus Production to Military Units. Accumulate -25% less war weariness than usual.  Training Yard gives +1 [ICON_Amenities] Amenity.', 'LOC_SLTH_POLICY_NATIONHOOD_DESCRIPTION', 'en_US'),
('Lothenar', 'LOC_CITY_SVARTALFAR_14_NAME', 'en_US'),
('Your mother visited me once, and cried for me. Tell her not to worry, there are worse here than I.', 'LOC_PEDIA_BUILDINGS_PAGE_BUILDING_CHANCERY_CHAPTER_HISTORY_PARA_3', 'en_US'),
('Shrine Of Sirona', 'LOC_BUILDING_CRISTO_REDENTOR_NAME', 'en_US'),
