('Alazkan looked back and smiled, "I don''t think were supposed to be here friend, what say we try to get out to real roads?"', 'LOC_PEDIA_BUILDINGS_PAGE_BUILDING_MONUMENT_CHAPTER_HISTORY_PARA_30', 'en_US'),
('Heradh', 'LOC_CITY_INFERNAL_12_NAME', 'en_US'),
('Gereth Minar', 'LOC_CITY_SVARTALFAR_2_NAME', 'en_US'),
('Gower considered the question. He only really wanted to see what was on the other side of the mountains, maybe wrestle the beasts he saw fighting on the plains. But this destruction, this kind of war, shocked him.', 'LOC_PEDIA_UNITS_PAGE_SLTH_UNIT_FAWN_CHAPTER_HISTORY_PARA_28', 'en_US'),
