('Arendel nodded. ', 'LOC_PEDIA_LEADERS_PAGE_SLTH_LEADER_ARENDEL_CHAPTER_HISTORY_PARA_14', 'en_US'),
('Anton Konal had been burning for nearly twenty hours.', 'LOC_PEDIA_UNITS_PAGE_SLTH_UNIT_PYRE_ZOMBIE_CHAPTER_HISTORY_PARA_1', 'en_US'),
