('The Savant peered into the flames before answering. "I have been ignored, mistreated, and scorned. Give me power to destroy my enemies!"', 'LOC_PEDIA_UNITS_PAGE_SLTH_UNIT_DISCIPLE_THE_ASHEN_VEIL_CHAPTER_HISTORY_PARA_8', 'en_US'),
